Peter Morris was devastated when his sister Claire died in a car crash in 1994 . 
  He believed she had been killed by her husband Malcolm Webster so he could cash in on her life insurance . 
  It took two decades for the truth to be revealed - Webster had drugged her and set her on fire . 
  He was jailed for life in 2011 and later tried to kill his second wife . 
  Peter and Claire appear on Britain's Darkest Taboos . 
 